{"tid":1328712,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底我應該點做","createTime":"2019-07-18T04:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T06:26:43.000Z","uid":128807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"980a2d42d76fc409840e501bf4f64786dc46e828","tid":1328712,"uid":128807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"同一班識左接近9年既朋友呢2年間開始越黎越多爭執 多數都係我1vN 當然我都有諗過係咪我有問題 始終佢地都企埋同一陣線同我拗 有時我講乜做乜都錯 其他人做就冇問題 有陣時會對我冷暴力 隨住種種原因 依家佢地既講下笑我已經分唔到係真定假 有時佢地疾下我我都冇咩問題 相反我疾返佢地 佢地就好似嬲嬲地 共同話題開始越黎越少 彼此既信任度都越黎越低 有時對住佢地會好攰 有時對我單單打打 我依家有時都唔想理佢地 wtsapp都唔想覆佢地 依家覺得係佢地面前我連笑既資格都無 係佢地眼中冇啱過<br />\n老實講我唔想冇咗呢班一齊咗咁耐既朋友<br />\n有無人可以教下我應該點做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 199<br />\n以上有啲感覺係我主觀覺得"},{"pid":"7fe71a7ea6332833cf0ee1861914e3a641b9b0fb","tid":1328712,"uid":75959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:12:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">保持獨立思考 唔好比敵人 輕易帶風向帶走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ae36f48c2311baa97fbe60dc7e1606728e314e6d","tid":1328712,"uid":128807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9debc19bf0e1a10b143f60d5da52b8d58c430eaf","tid":1328712,"uid":128807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9dd3ed726235478ec59140870b4625772ead44c","tid":1328712,"uid":128807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:46:58.000Z","msg":"pusg"},{"pid":"7caa5be76dfd009126444e10999ebb07bf866cea","tid":1328712,"uid":128807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:47:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"615b4b227e690eff31f4281f3471f4332af672ea","tid":1328712,"uid":128807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:11: